overview: For all those online-daters who have horror stories, "CRSHN ON U" is a stylish EDM nightmare date, glimpsing into the anonymity of online-dating and perils of modern-day courtship. Set in a surreal-noir world, C.O.U is a genre blender of horror, fashion and fantasy, wrapped up in a VFX-packed music video.
title: CRSHN ON U
